---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Jakob Figur | Technical Consultant & AI Engineer & Researcher"
  description="Technical Consultant & AI Engineer specializing in AI systems, strategic architecture, and technical transformation."
>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
      <h1 class="hero-headline" style="font-size: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Jakob Figur</h1>
      <p class="hero-subheadline" style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--primary-color); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        Technical Consultant @ Digistore24<br>AI Engineer & Researcher
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-secondary);">
        Bridging the gap between cutting-edge AI research and real-world business applications.
        I architect intelligent systems that transform how organizations operate, combining deep
        technical expertise with strategic business insight to deliver measurable impact.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Core Competencies -->
    <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">Core Competencies</h2>

    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-number">Pillar 01</div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">AI Systems Architecture</h3>
        <p class="pillar-content">
          Designing and implementing production-grade AI systems that scale. From proof-of-concept
          to enterprise deployment, I build robust architectures that handle real-world complexity
          while maintaining performance and reliability.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-number">Pillar 02</div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Strategic Technical Leadership</h3>
        <p class="pillar-content">
          Translating business objectives into technical roadmaps. I bridge the communication gap
          between C-suite stakeholders and engineering teams, ensuring AI initiatives deliver
          tangible ROI while building sustainable competitive advantages.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-number">Pillar 03</div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Research & Innovation</h3>
        <p class="pillar-content">
          Staying at the frontier of AI capabilities through active research and experimentation.
          I evaluate emerging technologies, conduct rigorous testing, and identify opportunities
          to leverage cutting-edge techniques for practical business applications.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-number">Pillar 04</div>
        <h3 class="pillar-title">Technical Transformation</h3>
        <p class="pillar-content">
          Orchestrating organization-wide technical evolution. I design and execute transformation
          strategies that modernize legacy systems, establish best practices, and build internal
          capabilities that enable teams to innovate independently.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <div class="philosophical-section" style="margin-top: 5rem;">
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Let's Connect</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        Interested in discussing AI strategy, technical architecture, or potential collaboration?
        I'm always open to conversations about pushing the boundaries of what's possible with AI.
      </p>
